folder: Victory Boulevard & Bryson Avenue, Staten Island, NY
text:
Victory Boulevard, at the N.E. corner of Bryson (formerly Decatur) Avenue. The inscription over the window reads: Carbureter Expert.

April 26, 1929

P. L. Sperr

folder: Victory Boulevard & Decatur Avenue, Staten Island, NY
text:
2444 Victory Boulevard, at the S.E. corner of Decatur Avenue, showing the A. Schultz residence (1932). The house was owned by F. Tritz in 1874 and by M. Mulvoney from 1898 to 1917.

May 19, 1932

P. L. Sperr
